    "servicesLead": "ZB Captures provides Pensacola real estate photography for agents, brokers, and property marketers who need MLS-ready photos, Zillow-ready images, HDR photography, drone photos, and social video that fit the expectations of Zillow, Homes.com, Redfin, Airbnb, and VRBO. Same-day availability is offered when the schedule allows.",
    "proofEyebrow": "Why agents book this",
    "proofTitle": "The Impact",
    "proofLead": "According to eye-tracking data, buyers spend 60% of their time looking at listing photos (compared to 20% at the description). On average, professional photos drive 61% more views to a listing, and reduce time on the market by 32%. Better photos also improve the perceived value of a home, increasing the sale price by up to $11,200 on average.",
